data.title: SENSATIONS – 09/01/08
data.text:
At Pure over the weekend: Jess Origliasso of "The Veronicas" and her on-again/off-again beau Azaria from "The Follow." Also there was former NBA pro Gary Payton.

Spotted at LAX: The Sugarhill Gang...

David Copperfield stopped in for a late night snack with a friend at Social House (Treasure Island)...

Hollywood socialite Susan Casden closed down Prive Las Vegas on Sunday night for her birthday, a celebration that included 300 guests, Elvis Impersonator Trent Carlini, a performance by burlesque star Dita Von Teese and a full concert by legendary band Journey. The party's encore included a performance by the Crazy Horse girls...

Burlesque star Dita Von Teese, hanging out with chef Kerry Simon Sunday night at CatHouse (Luxor) after her show...

Movie director Brett Ratner, spotted at Tryst nightclub Sunday inside Wynn Las Vegas...

At the opening party of ROK Vegas (New York-New York): chart-topper Katy Perry, performing for a crowd that included her boyfriend Travis McCoy ("Gym Class Heroes"), Shar Jackson, Brittany Snow and Jessica Stroup, co-stars of "Prom Night," Jenna Dewan and boyfriend Channing Tatum, Haylie Duff and Nick Zano, Josh Henderson ("Desperate Housewives"), Sean Huze ("In the Valley of Elah"), John Wilkes ("Red Jumpsuit Apparatus") and Jamie Chung (MTV’s"Real World San Diego")...

Paris and Nicky Hilton, dining at Wolfgang Puck's CUT (Palazzo) on Saturday evening...

Chris Rock, with friends at Joe’s Seafood, Prime Steak & Stone Crab (Forum Shops) before his sold-out show at Caesars Palace on Saturday...

Holly Madison, David Spade, Paul Oakenfold, Dana White, and Ron Jeremy, at the KISS show at The Pearl (Palms) on Friday...

Wayne Newton, dancing with friends at Blush boutique night on Saturday while celebrating a friend's wedding...

At "O" on Saturday: Mayor Oscar Goodman and Kourtney Kardashian, her boyfriend and friends...

At Saturday's grand opening of Paul Oakenfold's residency at Rain: actress Tara Reid and Chewy from the Chelsea Handler show...

At TAO Beach on Saturday: actress Christina Milian, oil heir Brandon Davis, actor Wilmer Valderrama and Pamela Anderson’s ex-husband Rick Salomon and MTV UK’s VJ Tim Cash...

Paris and Nicky Hilton, with their boyfriends Benji Madden and David Katzenberg as Wasted Space (Hard Rock Hotel) on Saturday...

At Body English (Hard Rock): E!'s Daily 10 co-hosts celebrated the birthday of Sal Masekela, who was greeted by Baron Davis of the Los Angeles Clippers, and Nicky Hilton and Katzenberg...

Actress Kristine Chenoweth of ABC’s "Pushing Daisies" with a large group of friends at Strip House...

Actor Carlo Rota (Fox’s "24") and girlfriend having an intimate dinner at KOI...

On the main stage At LAX (Luxor): Reality show star Khloe Kardashian, boxer Zab Judah, Shaun Phillips of the San Diego Chargers Larry Johnson of the Kansas City Chiefs, Rashad McCants of the Minnesota Timberwolves, Antoine Wright of the Dallas Mavericks, Damon Jones of the Milwaukee Bucks, and Juwon Howard of the Houston Rockets.

At Pure: actress Haylie Duff, actor Nick Zano, actor Channing Tatum and his "Step Up" costar Jenna Dewan. Also in the house: Larry Johnson and Shaun Phillips...

Actor/comedian David Spade and UFC president Dana White, at Tryst on Friday...

Frank Sinatra Jr., former Lt. Governor Lorraine Hunt-Bono and Dennis Bono, dining at The Steakhouse at Southpoint Hotel-Casino on Saturday...

Lance Burton, taking in Jeff McBride's new show "Magic at the Edge" at Palace Station. McBride was honored as "Magician of the Year" last week by the International Magicians Society...

Long-time Las Vegas publicist Steve Flynn, surprised with a 40th birthday party at the ESPN Zone. Guests in attendance, some of whom stepped up to roast the guest of honor, included Showtime Boxing analyst Al Bernstein, Top Rank executive Dena DuBeof, MGM Mirage boxing execs Scott Ghertner and Stephanie Heller. Flynn's mother, father, brother and two sisters flew in for the event...

Wilmer Valderrama, taking the mic at TAO early Sunday and revving up the crowd. Also there: Paris and Nicky Hilton with Jeff Beacher...
